if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('sys_adminlog')
and type = 'U')
drop table sys_adminlog
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sys_adminlog */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sys_adminlog (
AdminLogID int identity(1,1),
AdminID int not null default 0,
Type int not null default 0,
Content nvarchar(500) null default '',
OperateTime datetime not null default getdate(),
IP nvarchar(20) not null default '',
AppTime datetime not null default getdate(),
constraint PK_SYS_ADMINLOG primary key (AdminLogID)
)
go

if exists (select 1 from sys.extended_properties
where major_id = object_id('sys_adminlog') and minor_id = 0)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()

'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_adminlog'

end

'系统-管理员操作日志(OK)',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'sys_adminlog'
